title: StartMonologue
---
[wave] Welcome! [/wave] This room is your main hub - a calm place to plan, build, and prepare between café days.
But before anything else…  let’s take a look at your café space ☕
Walk to the highlighted Café Builder and press E to interact.
===

title: BuilderMonologue
---
This is your <place>Blueprint Builder</place>.Here you can remove, place, and rotate everything in your café.
Hmm… it looks a bit rough right now 😅 Let’s clean things up first.
Press <key>X</key> to enter <action>Remove Mode</action>. While in this mode, Left Click objects to remove them.
Remove <important>X objects</important> to continue.    
===

title: PlaceMonologue
---
Much better already ✨ Now it’s time to place furniture back and shape your café.
Press <key>X</key> again to exit <action>Remove Mode</action>. Open the <ui>All</ui> tab to see everything you own.
Select an object, then Left Click to place it in the café. Place <important>X objects</important> to continue. Make it cozy!!
===

title: BuyMonologue
---
A café needs supplies! 🛒
To brew coffee or unlock new furniture, you’ll need to visit the <place>Shop</place>.
Here you can buy ingredients, decorations and machines for your café.
Buy <important>10 Coffee Beans</important> to prepare for your first day.
===

title: DoorMonologue
---
Everything’s set — time to open! 🚪
Walk to the <place>highlighted door</place> and press <key>E</key> to <action>enter your café</action>.
This will start your first day as a café owner ☕
===

title: CafeIntroMonologue
---
Welcome to your café ☕✨ This is where the magic happens :3
You’ll serve customers, make drinks and grow your cozy little business. (MAKE MONEEEEEY AND FREINDS!!)
Let's wait for our first customer!
===

title: NPCMonologue
---
Here comes your first customer! 🎉
Customers will only arrive if there’s a seat available, so make sure your café has enough chairs.
Press <key>E</key> to <action>interact</action> and see what they want to order.
Prepare their drink at the <place>coffee machine</place>. Be quick — their <important>patience bar</important> appears above their head.
With some of them, you can also <action>chat</action> to build friendship!
===

title: RecipeBookMonologue
---
Not sure how to make a drink? 📖
Press <key>TAB</key> to open your <ui>Recipe Book</ui>. Here you can see all unlocked recipes and the ingredients needed for each one.
On the left side, you’ll find active customer orders. Click an order to view its recipe instantly.
===
title: MakeCoffeeMonologue
---
Let’s brew your first coffee ☕
First, grab a mug and ingredients
from the <place>highlighted storage drawer</place>. Press <key>E</key> to open it and select you Item. Then walk to the <place>coffee machine</place>.
While holding an item, press <key>E</key> to <action>add it to the machine</action>. And there you go — your first coffee! 🎉
(Later on, recipes will become more complex and exciting. There is a lot to unlock!)
===
title: EndMonologue
---
Each café day ends after some time 🌙 .. There’s a day and night cycle, and customers depend on the time of day.
Once all guests leave, you’ll see a daily recap of your progress. After that, the door back to the hub unlocks.
.. And don’t forget — <important>every Sunday</important>, rent is due! ..
That’s all you need to know. Enjoy your first day and have fun ☕💛
===
